lead_paragraph: Donald Trump is personally liable for operating a for-profit investment school without the required license, a New York judge ruled in a lawsuit brought by the New York Attorney General against the real estate entrepreneur.

headline.main: New York Judge Finds Donald Trump Liable for Unlicensed School
